name: Analyst Warns of BTC Dipping Below $100K as Gold-to-Bitcoin Rotation Takes Shape
description: The porcelain saint kneels in the decaying nave, overseeing the sacred noise of the transfer. Molten amber, the sacrifice of kings, is violently pulled into volumetric data-light ribbons. The kinetic choreography of tightening liquidity enacts the brutal liturgy of rebirth.
